{"tid":1633571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨鐵要停荃灣綫但隻字不提係因為黨鐵撞車","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:35:20.000Z","uid":9116,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2400ab57b04c6385ac420911062677150c8f76","tid":1633571,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"此訊息發放時間 : 2019-10-07 06:16<br />\n<br />\n由於港鐵整個網絡內大部分車站被嚴重破壞，仍需要暫時關閉以進行復修，為了騰出更多時間讓工程人員繼續復修工作，列車服務亦會提早於晚上6時結束。<br />\n <br />\n荃灣綫列車服務暫停；<br />\n <br />\n觀塘綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，黃埔、何文田、油麻地、旺角、太子、樂富、黃大仙、九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘及調景嶺站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n港島綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，西營盤、上環、金鐘、灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后及炮台山站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n南港島綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，金鐘站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n將軍澳綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，調景嶺、將軍澳、坑口、寶琳及康城站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n東涌綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，欣澳及東涌站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n迪士尼綫列車服務暫停;<br />\n <br />\n東鐵綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，大圍、沙田、大埔墟、粉嶺及上水站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n馬鞍山綫列車服務暫停；<br />\n <br />\n西鐵綫列車服務維持8分鐘一班，尖東、荃灣西、元朗、天水圍及屯門站暫時關閉；<br />\n <br />\n我們會因應實際情況實施客流管理措施或作出車務調動，包括關閉車站出入口、列車不停車站，或關閉車站等。<br />\n <br />\n有關最新的車務安排，請留意港鐵網頁、MTR Mobile、車站及列車廣播，以及傳媒發放的資訊。<br />\n <br />\n請乘客預早計劃行程，感謝您的體諒。<br />\n <br />\n+港鐵現正提供免費接駁巴士來往堅尼地城站和海洋公園站。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講撚咗一大輪但冇提過係因為撞車都停埋荃灣綫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20191007&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20782479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191007%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20782479&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=72f31106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191007%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20782479&h=a5132396\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20191007&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20782479</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365331&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=36515525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365331&h=165e1f70\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365331</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】港鐵荔景站往美孚站列車撞到路軌旁的石屎躉，八人受傷，荃灣綫因此全綫暫停，車長已暫停調離駕駛職務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵列車撞到路軌旁石屎躉，列車停在管道內。車上當時有大批乘客，乘客由消防員協助離開車廂，沿管道疏散返回荔景站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，荔景站一列列車經特別路線往美孚站時，未有在停車位置前按燈號停車，以時速約十公里撞到軌旁的石屎躉，六名乘客及兩名職員受傷，其他乘客陸續離開車站。<br />\n<br />\n有車上乘客表示，當時列車忽然煞停。"},{"pid":"5e023617ef220d6dd87eb113ed52675adffaefa4","tid":1633571,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d904237076a9d93b186bd67d184738f6e36532c5","tid":1633571,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"0ff1a24efdb545f6933111812016bc242e63c70e","tid":1633571,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"去柒咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a551c7370be0f99e584bee5026e2d96f33ab4fb0","tid":1633571,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"推呀！唔好畀黨鐵推卸責任"},{"pid":"56bc6db800465af4061dd63a4e3da0aa7119a768","tid":1633571,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}